:<font size="15">דּן</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
דּן / dân / dawn

===Etymology===
From [[דּין]] {{HH|1777}}; judge; 

===Proper noun===
'''דּן'''

# Dan, one of the sons of [[Jacob]]; also the tribe descended from him, and its territory; likewise a place in [[Palestine]] colonized by them: - [[Dan]].

